      "clause_number": "5.1",
      "kind": "numbered",
      "page": 2,
      "paragraph_index": 7,
      "text": "5.1. Bring the provisions of this circular to the notice of all the entities whose securities are\nlisted in the stock exchange and also to disseminate the same on its website.",
